responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "012882434E48BE28C99398A767774741", "Lo\'ha, Buno Ochoa, and Greetings! I am Vael Alaric, purveyor of lost trinkets from the many realms of Verra. Might I interest you in a rusty dagger from the Defiled Shores or mayhaps a skull goblet from the jungle dens of Go\'Koga?")
